quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,Nyene Imigisha myinshi
  55,2,Yigishije iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu
  55,3,Yaremye ikiremwa muntu
  55,4,Nuku mwigisha kuvuga
  55,5,Izuba n’Ukwezi bigira kugiharuro cayo
  55,6,N’ibiti bito bito na bininiya vyose bigamburukira Imana
  55,7,"N’Amajuru\tyose\tniyo\tyayadugije\thejuru\tn’ukuzishira\tk’uburinganire bungana"
  55,8,Kugira ngo ntimuhemuke mu gupima ku minzani yanyu
  55,9,Rero ni mupime kubipimo vy’ukuri kandi ntimu gabanye kuri iyo minzani
  55,10,N’Isi yayishize ho kubera ibiremwa vyiwe
  55,11,Muriyo harimwo ivyamwa hamwe n’imitende yegeranye kuyindi
  55,12,Harimwo n’ibifungurwa vy’intete bifise ibishishwa hamwe n’ibifungurwa bifise akamoto keza
  55,13,"Mwebwe\tbiremwa\tbantu\tbo\tmubwoko\tbubiri,\tni\tiyihe\tmigisha y’Umuremyi wanyu muhakana"
  55,14,Yaremye umuntu imukuye mw’ivu ry’ibumba nkakumwe kw’ibikoresho ry’ibumba
  55,15,Arema ibisigo akoresheje ururimi rw’umuriro
  55,16,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,17,"Umuremyi\tw’useruko\tbubiri\tn’Umuremyi\tw’uburengera\tzuba\tuko\tari bubiri"
  55,18,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,19,Niyo yahujije ibiyaga bibiri
  55,20,Hagati y’avyo hariho uruzitiro rutinjirana n’ayandi mazi
  55,21,None n’iyihe migisha y’umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,22,Muri ivyo biyaga uko ari bibiri harimwo ibisharizo vyiza vyitiriwe Ilulu hamwe n’ibindi vyitiriwe Mar’jani
  55,23,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,24,"Vyose biri kw’itegeko ryayo kuri ibi vyakozwe bigira\tmubiyaga umengo n’imisozi"
  55,25,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,26,N’ibiri hejuru y’Isi hamwe n’Amajuru vyose bizo zimangana
  55,27,"Hasigare ukwamaho kw’Umuremyi wawe, nyene iteka, n’urupfasoni"
  55,28,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,29,"Bimusaba ibiri mu majuru no kw’Isi ibirimwo vyose n’imisi yose, nayo ikaba iri mubindi bintu"
  55,30,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,31,Ubu vuba tuzoba kurikirana mwebwe ngabo uko muri babiri
  55,32,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,33,"Mwebwe miryango y’ibisigo n’abantu, nimwa shobora kwinyuvya ngo mwinjire mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi, rero ni mwinyuvye, mugabo ntimuzo kwinyuvya atari kububasha bwanje"
  55,34,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,35,"Muzoshikirizwa\turubeya\trw’umuriro\tw’umujumpu,\tnamwe\tntimuzo shobora kwikingira nawo"
  55,36,None n’iyihe migisha y’umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,37,"Nimwibuke\tigihe\tAmajuru\tazosenyagurika\tagaca\taba\tnk’agahama k’urushato rwatukuye"
  55,38,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,39,Kuri uwo musi nta muntu azobazwa kubijanye n’ibicumuro vyiwe canke mubisigo
  55,40,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,41,"Bazo\tmenyekana\tabantu\tbabi\tkubimenyetso\tvyabo,\thanyuma\tbaze bafatwe kumishatsi y’imitwe y’abo y’ubuhori hori no kumaguru yabo"
  55,42,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,43,Uwu niwa muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu waba bahakanyi bahora bahakana
  55,44,"Bazohora bakikuza hambavu\tyuwo muriro udahera no hambavu y’amazi ashushe abira nk’amarike"
  55,45,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,46,"N’uwutinya guhagarikwa imbere y’Umuremyi wiwe azoronka\timirima ibiri"
  55,47,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,48,N’imirima irimwo ibiti bifise amashami menshi cane
  55,49,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,50,Muriyo harimwo amasoko abiri y’amazi ahitamwo iyo myonga neza cane
  55,51,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,52,Muri iyo mirima harimwo ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bubiri bubiri n’uburenga
  55,53,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,54,"Bazoba\tbegamiye\tk’ubusaswa\tbushashweko\tibitambara\tvyoroshe n’ibiremereye. hamwe n’ivyamwa vyo muri iyo mirima icundereye hafi"
  55,55,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,56,"Hazoba\tharimwo\tabagore\tbahumurije\tamaso\tyabo,\tbakaba batarakorwako n’umuntu uwariwe wese imbere yabo canke ibisigo"
  55,57,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,58,Ninkuko abo bapfasoni basayangana nk’ubutare bwitiriwe Yaquuti na Mar’jaani
  55,59,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,60,Ntandishi y’ubugizi bw’ineza atari ukuriha ineza kuyindi
  55,61,None n’iyihe migisha y’umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,62,"No hejuru y’ivyo vyose, hariho n’iyindi mirima ibiri"
  55,63,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,64,Ifise amabara meza y’urwatsi rutoto ruhiye neza
  55,65,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,66,"Harimwo\tamasoko\tabiri\ty’amazi\tayo\tmazi\tavamwo\tn’inguvu\tnyinshi cane"
  55,67,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,68,"Harimwo ibiti vy’ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose, cane cane ibiti vy’imitende hamwe n’imikoma manga"
  55,69,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,70,Harimwo n’abapfasoni beza beza
  55,71,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,72,"Bafise amaso yera derere kandi meza manini maniniya kubaguma\tbari mu mazu y’abo gusa"
  55,73,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,74,Abo bapfasoni nti barakorwako n’umuntu uwariwe wese imbere y’abo canke ibisigo
  55,75,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,76,"Bazo\tkwegamira\tkunyegamo\tz’urwatsi\trutoto\tno\thejuru\ty’ubusaswa bwiza cane"
  55,77,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,78,"Rira\tninahajwe\tizina\rry’Umuremyi\rwawe,\rnyene\riteka\tn’urupfasoni\rruyikwiye"